import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]

    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', bins=30, color='blue', kde=True)
    plt.axvline(data['delay'].median(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Median: {data['delay'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.xlabel('Delay (minutes)')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight delays?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.boxplot(data=data, y='distance')
    avg_distance = data['distance'].mean()
    plt.axhline(avg_distance, color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Average Distance: {avg_distance:.2f}')
    plt.title('What is the average distance of flights?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data_grouped = data.groupby(['origin', 'destination']).size().reset_index(name='count')
    data_grouped = data_grouped.sort_values('count', ascending=False).head(10)

    chart = sns.barplot(x='origin_destination', y='count', data=data_grouped, palette='viridis')
    plt.title('What is the most common origin and destination for flights?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Origin-Destination')
    plt.ylabel('Number of Flights')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend(title='Origin-Destination', loc='upper right', labels=data_grouped['origin_destination'])

    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.scatterplot(data=data, x='distance', y='delay', hue='origin', palette='viridis')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between delay time and distance?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend(title='Origin', bbox_to_anchor=(1.05, 1), loc='upper left')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
